# zidecar deployment

## single node (personal)

    zidecar --zebrad-rpc http://127.0.0.1:8232

## single node with caddy (public)

    ZIDECAR_DOMAIN=zcash.example.com caddy run --config Caddyfile.zidecar

## HA pair

    DNS A records → caddy-01 IP, caddy-02 IP

    on each caddy node:

    ZIDECAR_DOMAIN=zcash.example.com \
    ZIDECAR_BACKENDS="zidecar-01:50051 zidecar-02:50051" \
    caddy run --config Caddyfile.zidecar

    on each zidecar node:

    zidecar --zebrad-rpc http://local-zebrad:8232 \
            --listen 0.0.0.0:50051 \
            --mempool-cache-ttl 3

## zclid (wallet daemon)

    # start daemon
    zclid --endpoint https://zcash.rotko.net

    # zcli connects automatically to 127.0.0.1:9067
    zcli balance    # instant, no sync
    zcli notes      # shows pending mempool activity

## systemd

    cp zidecar.service /etc/systemd/system/
    cp zclid.service /etc/systemd/user/
    systemctl enable --now zidecar
    systemctl --user enable --now zclid
